tpm_id <- "syn12223748"

tpm_df <- tpm_id %>% 
    create_df_from_synapse_id 

tpm_m <- tpm_df %>% 
    df_to_matrix("Hugo") %>% 
    .[,order(colnames(.))]

ltpm_df <- tpm_m %>% 
    add(1) %>% 
    log10 %>% 
    matrix_to_df("Hugo")

ltpm_matrix_tranpose <- ltpm_df %>% 
    df_to_matrix("Hugo") %>% 
    t

annotation_df <- ltpm_matrix_tranpose %>% 
    matrix_to_df("sample") %>% 
    select(sample) %>% 
    mutate(cell_type = str_match(sample, "([:print:]*)_BGI[:print:]*")[,2]) %>% 
    mutate(sample_n = str_match(sample, "[:print:]*_BGI_([:print:]*)")[,2]) %>% 
    as.data.frame %>% 
    column_to_rownames("sample") 
annotation_df2 <- annotation_df %>% 
    rownames_to_column("sample") %>% 
    as_data_frame %>% 
    select(-sample_n)

density_df <- ltpm_df %>% 
    select(-Hugo) %>% 
    gather(key = "sample", value = "value", CD4_T_cells_BGI:Monocytes_BGI_output3) %>% 
    left_join(annotation_df2)
## Joining, by = "sample"
p <- density_df %>% 
    ggplot(aes_string(x = "value", linetype = "sample", color = "cell_type")) +
    geom_density() +
    theme_bw() +
    xlab("Log10 Gene TPM") 

print(p)

autoplot(
    prcomp(ltpm_matrix_tranpose), 
    data = annotation_df, 
    shape = "cell_type", 
    colour = "sample_n",
    size = 6,
    main = "PCA") +
    scale_shape_manual(values = 22:24) +
    theme_bw() 

cor_matrix <- cor(tpm_m)
corrplot(cor_matrix, method = "ellipse")

tpm_m_transpose <- t(tpm_m)
clusters <- hclust(dist(tpm_m_transpose))
plot(clusters)
